        <div class="item-page pages_nos_metiers">
         <article class="bfc-post">
          <h2 class="bfc-postheader">
           Brokerage
          </h2>
          <div class="bfc-postcontent clearfix">
           <div class="bfc-article">
            <p>
             Atlas Capital Bourse is a Brokerage company approved by the Ministry of Finance since the 25
             <sup>
              th
             </sup>
             October, 2002.
            </p>
            <p>
             Atlas Capital Bourse's team includes dedicated professionals with an extensive experience on capital markets and finance in general, specializing in the following areas :
            </p>
            <ul>
             <li>
              Brokerage
             </li>
             <li>
              Syndication
             </li>
             <li>
              Investment Advisory
             </li>
             <li>
              Custody (trades clearing, dividend payments, stock splits, …)
             </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
             The Team offers to its clients a day-to-day trading platform characterized by efficient execution, diligent processing and absolute discretion.
            </p>
           </div>
          </div>
         </article>
        </div>
